snippet.title: Ambers Lawyer Having Hard Time In Court!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard's Lawyer Elaine Bredehoft was having a hard time with questioning Dr. Shannon Curry during day 9 of the Johnny Depp vs Amber Heard defamation lawsuit.  The objection was to speculation and she could not get over it.  I think her brain fried a little.  Rumors say she left Amber's legal team so she will be one lawyer down.
